item.title: Sitatbyoot
item.description: Sitatbyoot seeks to empower women and help them enter the labor market from their homes, as it encourages women to sell their products on demand. The site also provides video tutorials that help employers ensure the quality of work provided by members of Sitatbyoot .

item.title: Cura Healthcare
item.description: Cura is the first app in the middle east and turkey that offers telemedicine and medical consultations directly of your smartphone. 24/7 on demand-doctors and specialties to help you and your family anytime, anywhere.
